  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Overview</h2>Is there a back story? No... The adventure is yours to make! Pick a character, and you are dropped into the fantasy middle ages to start your journey!<br>This game is designed for you to quickly jump right into it and begin hacking and slashing your way through!<br><br>I initially created this game to troll my friend, but it has since evolved into something substantial and fun that I'm now sharing with the world!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Procedure generated world for countless explorations!<br></li><li>NPCs to trade with, and potentials to improve your relationship for enlisting them!<br></li><li>Build & place walls, workbenches, chests, traps and so many more to aid your quests! <br></li><li>Over 40 varieties of enemies!<br></li><li>Choose your starting character but level and master yours skills however you see fit!<br></li><li>Bring your friends along for the adventure! (Co-op instructions below)</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >LAN Co-op</h2>To invite and play with friends, we recommend using Hamachi<br>Both you and your friends will need to install Hamachi. Once installed, please create a network group and invite your friends.<br>Lastly, use the IPv4 address generated by Hamachi for hosting and connecting.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Highlights</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695400/extras/8e840d34f45730514a1335a2f003de11.poster.avif?t=1710953797\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695400/extras/8e840d34f45730514a1335a2f003de11.webm?t=1710953797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695400/extras/8e840d34f45730514a1335a2f003de11.mp4?t=1710953797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695400/extras/79e6688121e67568ac7bf01363f95b1c.poster.avif?t=1710953797\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695400/extras/79e6688121e67568ac7bf01363f95b1c.webm?t=1710953797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695400/extras/79e6688121e67568ac7bf01363f95b1c.mp4?t=1710953797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695400/extras/25995a1bc5bf65ea2634453b257db4bd.poster.avif?t=1710953797\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695400/extras/25995a1bc5bf65ea2634453b257db4bd.webm?t=1710953797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695400/extras/25995a1bc5bf65ea2634453b257db4bd.mp4?t=1710953797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Overview</h2>Is there a back story? No... The adventure is yours to make! Pick a character, and you are dropped into the fantasy middle ages to start your journey!<br>This game is designed for you to quickly jump right into it and begin hacking and slashing your way through!<br><br>I initially created this game to troll my friend, but it has since evolved into something substantial and fun that I'm now sharing with the world!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Procedure generated world for countless explorations!<br></li><li>NPCs to trade with, and potentials to improve your relationship for enlisting them!<br></li><li>Build & place walls, workbenches, chests, traps and so many more to aid your quests! <br></li><li>Over 40 varieties of enemies!<br></li><li>Choose your starting character but level and master yours skills however you see fit!<br></li><li>Bring your friends along for the adventure! (Co-op instructions below)</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >LAN Co-op</h2>To invite and play with friends, we recommend using Hamachi<br>Both you and your friends will need to install Hamachi. Once installed, please create a network group and invite your friends.<br>Lastly, use the IPv4 address generated by Hamachi for hosting and connecting.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Highlights</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695400/extras/8e840d34f45730514a1335a2f003de11.poster.avif?t=1710953797\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695400/extras/8e840d34f45730514a1335a2f003de11.webm?t=1710953797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695400/extras/8e840d34f45730514a1335a2f003de11.mp4?t=1710953797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695400/extras/79e6688121e67568ac7bf01363f95b1c.poster.avif?t=1710953797\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695400/extras/79e6688121e67568ac7bf01363f95b1c.webm?t=1710953797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695400/extras/79e6688121e67568ac7bf01363f95b1c.mp4?t=1710953797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695400/extras/25995a1bc5bf65ea2634453b257db4bd.poster.avif?t=1710953797\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695400/extras/25995a1bc5bf65ea2634453b257db4bd.webm?t=1710953797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2695400/extras/25995a1bc5bf65ea2634453b257db4bd.mp4?t=1710953797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
